site_name: Land At Cooper St Burke St Lawrence St Bothwell Close And
description: Request for a Scoping Opinion in accordance with Regulation 15 of the Town and Country Planning (Environmental Impact Assessment)(England) Regulations 2017 (as amended) in relation to the Site known as Canning Town Estate Regeneration Masterplan for the retention / refurbishment and / or demolition of the existing buildings on site and the phased construction of residential-led mixed-use development. The Proposed Development will comprise up to 1,350 new residential dwellings (Use Class C3), up to approximately 2,000m2 of non-residential floorspace (Use Class E (a/b/c/d/g) / F1 / F2) with associated servicing, public open space and landscaping.
